attr.title: Corsairs
attr.desc: J2ME pirate trading and naval combat game originally developed by Akella for Nokia 6230i. Trade, sail, and fight naval battles in a pixel-art Caribbean setting. Includes English translation (original game is Russian only).
attr.inst: Place the original Corsairs JAR as corsairs.jar into ports/corsairs/. The game JAR can be found in J2ME game archives.
attr.inst_md: Place the original Corsairs JAR as `corsairs.jar` into `ports/corsairs/`. The game JAR can be found in J2ME game archives.
